                <h1>Statement of Intent</h1>
                <p>I interpreted “The Birds” by Daphne du Maurier as a story about war. Specifically, the humans are on
                    one side of the war, getting overwhelmed by the birds. Therefore, I thought that creating a memorial
                    website for this “war” was fitting. I created this memorial website to humanize those that were
                    impacted by this war, incorporating characters shown in the horror movie version of "The Birds"
                    released in 1963. There were various individual choices that were made through the reaction of this
                    website. </p>
